{"tid":1877874,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"毒娥有種別求醫 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-02-13T09:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T09:26:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bfdf42697088467e580b3877cdd45a7440a4d4","tid":1877874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200213/20861198/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200213%2F20861198%2F&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=2575e4bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200213%2F20861198%2F&h=6bb367a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200213/20861198/</a><br />\n<br />\n毒娥有種別求醫 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200213/large/1581492160_14d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200213%2Flarge%2F1581492160_14d0.jpg&h=ead911a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自2月8號起，14日強制檢疫令形同虛設，仍hea做欺騙市民，全無阻嚇力，因「冇掩雞籠」般放縱，疫情蔓延確診個案日增。<br />\n<br />\n社會播毒人人自危，毒娥仍死不全面封關，反以「無咩意思」為由拒絕，更聲稱現時若要封，就是「封貨運」（其實她已阻截封殺口罩了）──又用語言偽術來轉移視線偷換概念恐嚇港人了，大家支持醫護罷工，目標指向全面封關堵截病毒源頭，是封人驅疫，關貨運什麼事？一定有辦法解決「物」，不能與解決「人」混作一談。你自己精神病重，別當港人白癡，加以誣衊。<br />\n<br />\n如今步向疫埠，封關關鍵時期已過，益顯林鄭不忘仇恨、報復初心，就是要借疫殺死一批人特別是反對派，不止賣港還是毀港滅港，她在暗角心涼冷笑。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸放棄了武漢也放棄了湖北省，日夜燒屍全城烏煙霧霾，連北京上海廣州深圳也封城了，香港，是毒娥刻意不作為下最大的缺口，或許成為下一個武漢。<br />\n<br />\n狗官、黑警、貪蝗&hellip;&hellip;那麼愛國愛黨，有骨氣回大陸醫吧，尤其是林鄭毒娥，眾望所歸早日中招，有種別戴口罩，別求醫護救命，萬死難洗罪孽。<br />\n<br />\n前線醫護以港人優先，上述阻路佔資源的人渣，看着辦。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"1c970775bda0b46d1ec7b9395efce82e6333b1a9","tid":1877874,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"毒娥"},{"pid":"2de5ead20a9ba97da81200db7ad5eec60c6ec540","tid":1877874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:19:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"96fe76379f2c152fd7598c27ba4f9ed22d97c021","tid":1877874,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/9857851258/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F9857851258%2F0&h=edf60cd1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}